\begin_layout Enumerate
Sea 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1},A_{2},A_{3},\cdots$
\end_inset

 una serie numerable de eventos y sea 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $B_{1},B_{2},B_{3},\cdots$
\end_inset

otra serie numerable de eventos tal que 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B_{1}=A_{1},\;B_{2}=A_{1}^{\prime}\cap A_{2},\;B_{3}=A_{1}^{\prime}\cap A_{2}^{\prime}\cap A_{3}...
